::Stratus::

Stratus makes several circles around the ship before he recieves Astroblast's transmission.

"Got it," he replies, "The ship is tangled in vines. I'll chew them off while he gets here."

He swims over to one of the bigger vines holding the ship down, biting into it, though the taste was alien to his shark beast mode.
